    <div class="side-bar hidden md:block">
    <h2>Resistor Color Duo</h2>
    <p>Solutions to resistor-color-duo in various languages.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/exercism.html">Index</a></li>
    </ul>
    <ul><li><a href="#roc">Roc</a></li><li><a href="#c">C</a></li></ul>
